Now, how would you
demonstrate or manifest

00:13:48.390 --> 00:13:53.670
that person as masculine
with that same hand

00:13:53.670 --> 00:13:54.840
shape and movement?

00:13:54.840 --> 00:13:56.416
What would you do?

00:13:56.416 --> 00:13:56.916
[LAUGHTER]

00:13:56.916 --> 00:13:57.416
Ha.

00:13:57.416 --> 00:14:01.370
You wouldn't do it by your
head, because that actually

00:14:01.370 --> 00:14:05.240
would mean you're
walking on the head.

00:14:05.240 --> 00:14:06.710
Be careful with the location.

00:14:06.710 --> 00:14:09.440
Location, location
is everything.

00:14:09.440 --> 00:14:15.370
So how would you express
and demonstrate masculinity?

00:14:15.370 --> 00:14:16.516
How would you do it?

00:14:16.516 --> 00:14:19.920
[LAUGHTER]

00:14:19.920 --> 00:14:22.865
Well you're kind of cheating
doing two hands at once there.

00:14:22.865 --> 00:14:23.970
[LAUGHTER]

00:14:23.970 --> 00:14:24.470
OK.

00:14:24.470 --> 00:14:26.100
So you're adding those
facial expressions,

00:14:26.100 --> 00:14:27.142
those non-manual markers.

00:14:27.142 --> 00:14:31.190
[LAUGHTER]

00:14:31.190 --> 00:14:35.600
You see how crucial it was
