and how they identify?

00:14:36.620 --> 00:14:40.470
[LAUGHTER]

00:14:40.470 --> 00:14:44.810
Now what about a female?

00:14:44.810 --> 00:14:46.910
In a feminine way,
how would you do that?

00:14:46.910 --> 00:14:47.810
[LAUGHTER]

00:14:47.810 --> 00:14:51.379
Same sign, same hand shape,
show me what you got.

00:14:51.379 --> 00:14:52.876
[INTERPOSING VOICES]

00:14:52.876 --> 00:14:56.370
[LAUGHTER]

00:14:56.370 --> 00:14:58.860
- See the difference?

00:14:58.860 --> 00:15:03.480
So again, back to those
fundamental parameters.

00:15:03.480 --> 00:15:06.050
This is what I live
and breathe in my work

00:15:06.050 --> 00:15:08.390
as a performer and an artist.

00:15:08.390 --> 00:15:10.880
How I can manipulate
these parameters,

00:15:10.880 --> 00:15:16.220
those hand shapes, movement,
location, orientation,

00:15:16.220 --> 00:15:19.940
and facial expressions, to
