00:15:24.290 --> 00:15:28.350
system, my culture, all in one.

00:15:28.350 --> 00:15:28.850
Thank you.

00:15:28.850 --> 00:15:56.727
[APPLAUSE]

00:15:56.727 --> 00:15:58.310
- Before we get on
to my presentation,

00:15:58.310 --> 00:16:00.890
I just want to share
a few disclaimers.

00:16:00.890 --> 00:16:04.710
For this, I will be using
American Sign Language

00:16:04.710 --> 00:16:06.750
and English, but I
want to recognize

00:16:06.750 --> 00:16:09.480
